<doc id="367117" wikidata="Q1945477" url="?curid=367117" title="Montafonerbahn">
<text>The Montafonerbahn (&quot;Montafon Railway&quot;, MBS) is a privately owned railway company that primarily operates services from Bregenz to Schruns, via Bludenz. The company is headquartered in Schruns.

