* Leigh Blackmore. &quot;Sandalwood and Jade: The Weird and Fantastic Verse of Linwood Vrooman Carter.&quot; &quot;Dead Reckonings&quot; 28 (Fall 2020) Eds. Alex Houstoun and Michael J. Abolafia.

